coverage.logic
Class BiExpression

java.lang.Object
  coverage.logic.Expression
      coverage.logic.BiExpression

public class BiExpression
extends Expression

It is the binary expression class. It includes five logic operators: equivalence, implication, exclusive or, or, and.
